This biotechnology company expanded its board to six members with the addition of three outside directors: Elliot H. Stein, Raymond J. Kalinowski Sr. and Theodore M. Armstrong.
Mr. Stein is chairman emeritus of Stifel Financial Corp., Mr. Kalinowski is vice chairman of A.G. Edwards Inc. and Mr. Armstrong is senior vice president for finance and administration and chief financial officer of Angelica Corp. 

